<item>
  <title>nvim im select remote 在远程机器上丝滑切换输入法</title>
  <link>https://williamlfang.github.io/2025-01-10-nvim-im-select-remote-%E5%9C%A8%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E6%9C%BA%E5%99%A8%E4%B8%8A%E4%B8%9D%E6%BB%91%E5%88%87%E6%8D%A2%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%E6%B3%95/</link>
  <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 00:36:18 &#43;0800</pubDate>
  <author>william</author>
  <guid>https://williamlfang.github.io/2025-01-10-nvim-im-select-remote-%E5%9C%A8%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E6%9C%BA%E5%99%A8%E4%B8%8A%E4%B8%9D%E6%BB%91%E5%88%87%E6%8D%A2%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%E6%B3%95/</guid>
  <description><![CDATA[<p><code>im-select.nvim</code> 解决了在本地机器的终端上面丝滑切换中英文输入法。但是我回到家里，需要连接到公司的远程服务器，然后再登录
我的 <code>tmux</code> 回话，即可快速返回下班前的工作状态了。这时候如果需要在 <code>tmux</code> 使用 <code>vim</code> 进行中文输入，就
无法再使用 <code>im-select</code> 的切换功能了，因为其使用使用的是本地的输入法切换，在远程环境中，无法调用。</p>
<p>这时候我发现一个可以让 <code>nvim</code> 远程调用本地的输入法切换命令：</p>
<ul>
<li>一旦进入 <code>insert</code> 模式，就从远程发送一个命令给本地，要求切换到中文输入法</li>
<li>一旦退出 <code>insert</code> 模式（即按下 <code>Esc</code>），再从远程发送一个命令给本地，要求切换到英文，这样就可以在 <code>normal</code> 模式下使用各种按键了。</li>
</ul>]]></description>
</item>
<item>
  <title>nvim im select</title>
  <link>https://williamlfang.github.io/2025-01-08-nvim-im-select/</link>
  <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 23:43:01 &#43;0800</pubDate>
  <author>william</author>
  <guid>https://williamlfang.github.io/2025-01-08-nvim-im-select/</guid>
  <description><![CDATA[<p>使用 <code>vim</code> 进行中文输入，遇到的最大困难是要频繁的切换中英文，这个操作是比较繁琐的，往往会打断创作思路。我们的想法是，在 <code>insert</code> 模式下，使用中文输入；但是在 <code>normal</code> 模式下，则自动切换到英文输入，如此可以方便各种键位的操作。</p>
<p>在网上找了一会，发现有一个 <code>im-select</code> 的插件可以实现这个目的，使用起来非常的丝滑。</p>]]></description>
</item>
<item>
  <title>crontab FAILED to authorize user with PAM</title>
  <link>https://williamlfang.github.io/2025-01-08-crontab-failed-to-authorize-user-with-pam/</link>
  <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 13:21:46 &#43;0800</pubDate>
  <author>william</author>
  <guid>https://williamlfang.github.io/2025-01-08-crontab-failed-to-authorize-user-with-pam/</guid>
  <description><![CDATA[<div class="featured-image"><img loading="eager" src="https://williamlfang.github.io/2025-01-08-crontab-failed-to-authorize-user-with-pam/failed.png" alt="crontab FAILED to authorize user with PAM" title="crontab FAILED to authorize user with PAM" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"/></div><p>这几天发现有一个 <code>crontab</code> 没有启动，一开始以为是脚本有问题，所以添加了日志重定向。可是还是没有任何输出，所以怀疑是 <code>crontab</code> 没有执行，然后查看系统日志 <code>/var/log/cron</code> 发现有报错</p>
<div class="highlight" id="id-1"><div class="chroma">
<table class="lntable"><tr><td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code><span class="lnt">1
</span></code></pre></td>
<td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"><span class="line"><span class="cl">crond<span class="o">[</span>81985<span class="o">]</span>: <span class="o">(</span>infra<span class="o">)</span> FAILED to authorize user with PAM <span class="o">(</span>Module is unknown<span class="o">)</span></span></span></code></pre></td></tr></table>
</div>
</div><p>在网上搜索发现是 <code>PAM</code> 密钥过期了，需要重新设置</p>
<div class="highlight" id="id-2"><div class="chroma">
<table class="lntable"><tr><td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code><span class="lnt">1
</span><span class="lnt">2
</span><span class="lnt">3
</span><span class="lnt">4
</span></code></pre></td>
<td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"><span class="line"><span class="cl">chage -M <span class="m">99999</span> root
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">chage -M <span class="m">99999</span> infra
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">chage -M <span class="m">99999</span> spd
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">chage -M <span class="m">99999</span> ops</span></span></code></pre></td></tr></table>
</div>
</div><p>重新查看就可以了</p>
<div class="highlight" id="id-3"><div class="chroma">
<table class="lntable"><tr><td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code><span class="lnt">1
</span><span class="lnt">2
</span><span class="lnt">3
</span><span class="lnt">4
</span><span class="lnt">5
</span><span class="lnt">6
</span><span class="lnt">7
</span><span class="lnt">8
</span></code></pre></td>
<td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"><span class="line"><span class="cl">chage -l infra
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">Last password change                                    : Jul 12, <span class="m">2024</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">Password expires                                        : never
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">Password inactive                                       : never
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">Account expires                                         : never
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">Minimum number of days between password change          : <span class="m">0</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">Maximum number of days between password change          : <span class="m">99999</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">Number of days of warning before password expires       : <span class="m">7</span></span></span></code></pre></td></tr></table>
</div>
</div>]]></description>
